Localization.Name: Gen Liberty Ale (Bottle)
Localization.Description:
HEI: 23
Effects: Cognitive Impairment, Dehydrating

Liberty Lake beer has been brewed by families on Terra for generations to provide a crisp, clean ale perfect to partake when you arrive at those little moments made to be spent enjoying life. Gen Liberty is a tart lactic ale perfect for warm nights.
